Show a report for a completed eval run

Usage: fastskill eval report [OPTIONS] --run-dir <RUN_DIR>

Options:
      --run-dir <RUN_DIR>  Path to the specific run directory
      --json               Output as JSON
  -h, --help               Print help

Examples:
  fastskill eval report --run-dir [TEMP_DIR]
